UMNUZ Thabani Nyawose onguSomlomo weTheku usazoqhubeka nokuqhoqhobala lesi sikhundla. Lokhu kulandela ukuthi inhlangano iphakamise ukungabethembi ubuholi bakhe ingasayinanga ukuthi kumele kudingidwe lolu daba, nayo igcine iveza ukuthi isazoxhumana nabammeli bayo ukuze ithole izeluleko zomthetho. Lesi siphakamiso sokungabethembi ubuholi bukaNyawose besifakwe yi-ADeC eholwa nguMnuz Visvin Reddy. Njengamanje kulindelwe ukuthi kuhlehle ukudingida lolu daba, sekuyoze lungene emhlanganweni olandelayo. Bekunamahlebezi athi namanye amalungu e-ANC ayathinteka emizameni yokuchitha uNyawose kodwa uMnuz Mlondi Mkhize okhulumela i-ANC ukuchithe konke lokho, wathi bona bayameseka uNyawose futhi wenza umsebenzi omuhle kubeni nguSomlomo weTheku. UReddy ubekhala ngokuthi uNyawose uyamhlula umsebenzi futhi uyawacindezele amaqembu aphikisayo uma ephakamisa kumbe eveza imibono yawo.